{
  "message": "fuzz(fj-conformance): add 46 corpus seeds expanding primitive coverage\n\nExtends fuzzer corpus from 40 to 88 seeds, covering 69 unique primitive\nindices (up from ~22). New seeds target:\n- Binary ops: Sub, Min, Pow, Rem\n- Unary math: Abs, Rsqrt, Floor, Ceil, Round, Cos, Tan, Sinh, Tanh\n- Transcendental: Expm1, Log1p, Reciprocal, Logistic, Erf, Erfc\n- Comparison: Eq, Lt, Gt\n- Bitwise: BitwiseAnd, BitwiseOr, BitwiseXor, BitwiseNot, ShiftLeft\n- Integer: PopulationCount, CountLeadingZeros\n- Reduction: ReduceSum, ReduceMax, ReduceMin, ReduceProd\n- Tensor ops: Reshape, Slice, Transpose, Concatenate, Rev, Squeeze\n- Advanced: OneHot, Cumsum, Cumprod, Sort, Argsort, Conv, ReduceWindow\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
